married couple
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:[sp. use; a rural labour unit]  married employees [where both wife and husband are involved in either shepherding, tractor-driving, milking, cooking, housekeeping or gardening. ]


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
